postcontent: I have a very lightly used Vortex Viper PST-14ST-A scope for sale. The glass is very clear and it is perfect for an AR platform rifle. It has a 1-4 magnification and works very well at close range with both eyes open or at longer ranges if you want to use the MIL dot for range and holdover. The dot and the circle are illuminated with adjustable brightness and it has a mil dot reticle. The clear glass and the adjustable reticle brightness work great in low light conditions. You never need to take your eye off your target while you search for the dial. The ONLY reason I am parting with this fine scope is because my eyesight and the reticle do not get along.
